  "_comment": "MO HealthNet (DSS/MHD). Migrated 2024 from manuals.momed.com → mydss.mo.gov. Most manuals are DOCX, not PDF (e.g. Physicians-Provider-Manual-Published-June-03-2026.docx, Home Health Provider Manual.docx); DME + Pharmacy benefit tables are PDF behind a pdf.js viewer iframe (?file=<encoded>). Direct file URLs are date-stamped and rotate — use the /media/ wrapper as the stable handle. No standalone Laboratory manual on the index (lab covered under Physician/Hospital). Managed-care plan manuals (Healthy Blue / Home State / UHC) live on plan sites — out of scope.",
